" any more email from us. Please do not reply to this e-mail; if you require "
"assistance, check the help section of the %(platform_name)s web site."
msgstr ""
"Ikiwa hukuitaka hili, huna haja ya kufanya chochote; hutapokea barua pepe "
"zaidi kutoka kwetu. Tafadhali usijibu barua pepe hii; ikiwa unahitaji "
"msaada, angalia sehemu ya msaada ya tovuti ya %(platform_name)s."

