"Please note that while assistance is available in most courses that offer verified certificates, a few courses and programs are not eligible. You must complete a separate application for each course you take. You may be approved for financial assistance five (5) times each year (based on 12-month period from you first approval). \n"
"To apply for financial assistance: \n"
"1. Enroll in the audit track for an eligible course that offers Verified Certificates. \n"
"2. Complete this application. \n"
"3. Check your email, please allow 4 weeks for your application to be processed."
msgstr ""
"Tunapanga kutumia taarifa hizi kutathmini maombi yako ya msaada wa kifedha na kuboresha programu yetu ya msaada wa kifedha. \n"
"Tafadhali kumbuka kwamba ingawa msaada unapatikana katika kozi nyingi zinazotoa vyeti vilivyothibitishwa, baadhi ya kozi na programu hazifai. Lazima ucomplete ombi tofauti kwa kila kozi unayochukua. Unaweza kuidhinishwa msaada wa kifedha mara tano (5) kila mwaka (kutokana na kipindi cha miezi 12 tangu idhinisho lako la kwanza). \n"
"Ili kuomba msaada wa kifedha: \n"
"1. Jiandikishe kwenye njia ya ukaguzi kwa kozi inayostahili inayotoa Vyeti Vilivyothibitishwa. \n"
"2. Kamilisha ombi hili. \n"
"3. Angalia barua pepe yako, tafadhali subiri wiki 4 ili ombi lako lisindike."

