" the configuration applies to all courses within that context. At most one "
"value can be set at a time.{br}If multiple contexts apply to a course (for "
"example, if configuration is specified for the course specifically, and for "
"the org that the course is in, then the more specific context overrides the "
"more general context."
msgstr ""
"Hizi zinaweka muktadha ambao mipangilio hii itafanyiwa kazi. Ikiwa hakuna "
"thamani zilizowekwa, basi mipangilio inatumika kwa viwango vyote. Ikiwa "
"thamani moja imewekwa, basi inahusu kozi zote ndani ya muktadha huo. Kwa "
"wakati mmoja, thamani moja tu inaweza kuwekwa.{br}Ikiwa muktadha mwingi "
"unahusu kozi (kwa mfano, ikiwa mipangilio imewekwa mahsusi kwa kozi na pia "
"kwa shirika ambalo kozi iko, basi muktadha maalum unachukua nafasi ya "
"muktadha wa jumla)."

#: openedx/core/djangoapps/config_model_utils/admin.py:53
msgid ""
"If any of these values are left empty or \"Unknown\", then their value at "
"runtime will be retrieved from the next most specific context that applies. "
"For example, if \"Enabled\" is left as \"Unknown\" in the course context, "
"then that course will be Enabled only if the org that it is in is Enabled."
msgstr ""
"Ikiwa thamani yoyote kati ya hizi itaachwa tupu au \"Unknown\", basi thamani"
" yao wakati wa utekelezaji itachukuliwa kutoka muktadha unaofaa zaidi "
"unaotumika. Kwa mfano, ikiwa \"Enabled\" itaachwa kama \"Unknown\" katika "
"muktadha wa kozi, basi kozi hiyo itawashwa Enabled ikiwa tu shirika linalo "
"katika kozi hilo limewezeshwa."

