msgstr ""
"Mpangilio huu unaonyesha kama wanafunzi wana muda mdogo wa kuangalia au "
"kuingiliana na kipengele hiki cha maudhui ya kozi."

#: xmodule/seq_block.py:162
msgid "Time Limit in Minutes"
